      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant body damage, including large dents and visible rust. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and several missing or broken components.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
